---
const avatarUrl = "/images/profile.jpeg";
---
<div class="welcome">
  <img src={avatarUrl} alt="我的头像" class="avatar" />
  <h1>你好，我是<a href="https://github.com/kotvaer" target="_blank">蓝染</a></h1>
  <p>
    一名后端开发工程师，对技术充满热情。我喜欢通过这个博客分享我的知识和经验。
  </p>
  <div class="buttons">
    <a href="/about" class="button">关于我</a>
    <a href="/blog" class="button-secondary">所有文章</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .avatar {
    width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 5px solid #ff9776;
    box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem; /* 保持底部间距 */
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .avatar:hover {
    transform: scale(1.08); /* 悬停时放大更多 */
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* 悬停时阴影更深 */
  }
  .welcome {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; /* 水平居中所有子元素 */
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background-color: transparent;
    transform: translateY(-120px); /* 向上移动 */
  }
  .welcome h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center; /* 确保h1内部文本居中 */
  }
  .welcome h1 a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }
  .welcome h1 a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .welcome p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    text-align: center; /* 确保p内部文本居中 */
  }
  .buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .button, .button-secondary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .button {
    background-color: #ff9776;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .button-secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 2px solid #ff9776;
    color: #ff9776;
  }
  .button:hover, .button-secondary:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  /* Dark mode adjustments */
  html.dark .welcome {
    background-color: transparent;
  }
  html.dark .button-secondary {
    color: #ff9776;
    border-color: #ff9776;
  }
</style>